                                                     :link     "https://shelf-awareness.com/readers-issue.html?issue=729#m12787"
                                                     :text     "Cindy Baldwin’s graceful debut is an ode to family and community. Hints of sweet magical realism touch Where the Watermelons Grow, balancing this exquisite novel’s bittersweet authenticity."}
