                                                     :link     "https://bookpage.com/reviews/22885-cindy-baldwin-where-watermelons-grow-childrens#.XNr5gaJKgWo"
                                                     :text     "...a spot-on, insightful novel about a preteen learning to live with and accept a parent’s mental illness."}
